                                team to stay up-to-date with what everybody is
                                working on," <a
                                    class="text-blue-600 decoration-2 hover:underline focus:outline-none focus:underline font-medium dark:text-blue-500"
                                    href="#">said</a
                                > Stewart Scott-Curran, Intercom's Director of Brand
                                Design.
                            </li>
                            <li class="ps-2">
                                Preline opened a new way of sharing. It's a
                                persistent way for everyone to see and absorb
                                each other's work," said David Scott, Creative
                                Director at <a
                                    class="text-blue-600 decoration-2 hover:underline focus:outline-none focus:underline font-medium dark:text-blue-500"
                                    href="#">Eventbrite</a
